HW2SIC   START   1000
FIRST    LDA     NUM1
         STA     SUM
         STA     TEMP
ADDLP    LDA     TEMP
         ADD     TWO
         STA     TEMP
         ADD     SUM
         STA     SUM
         LDA     TEMP
         ADD     TWO
         COMP    NUM2
         JEQ     ADDLP
         JLT     ADDLP
. 
. 
NUM1     WORD    15
NUM2     WORD    37
TEMP     RESW    1
SUM      RESW    1
TWO      WORD    2
         END     FIRST